mapper.expression:
{
  items_won: {{length(62.records)}},
  items_sold: {{length(63.records)}},
  total_revenue: {{sum(63.records[].fields.salePrice)}},
  total_profit: {{sum(63.records[].fields.finalProfit)}},
  active_listings: {{length(64.records)}},
  win_rate: {{if(length(62.records) > 0; divide(length(62.records); 100) * 100; 0)}},
  roi_percentage: {{if(sum(63.records[].fields.finalPrice) > 0; divide(sum(63.records[].fields.finalProfit); sum(63.records[].fields.finalPrice)) * 100; 0)}}
}

mapper.prompt:
Generate a comprehensive daily performance report for the Automated Auction Assistant:

Daily Statistics:
- Items Won: {{65.items_won}}
- Items Sold: {{65.items_sold}}
- Total Revenue: ${{65.total_revenue}}
- Total Profit: ${{65.total_profit}}
- ROI: {{round(65.roi_percentage; 1)}}%
- Win Rate: {{round(65.win_rate; 1)}}%
- Active Listings: {{65.active_listings}}

Top Performing Items Today:
{{map(take(sortBy(63.records; 'fields.finalProfit'; 'desc'); 3); 'fields.title')}}

Include:
1. Performance summary
2. Key insights and trends
3. Recommendations for tomorrow
4. Risk assessment
5. Action items

Format as professional business report.

mapper.content:
{{67.choices[1].message.content}}

---
Detailed Statistics:

Items Won Today: {{65.items_won}}
Items Sold Today: {{65.items_sold}}
Revenue: ${{65.total_revenue}}
Profit: ${{65.total_profit}}
ROI: {{round(65.roi_percentage; 1)}}%
Active Listings: {{65.active_listings}}

Top Sales Today:
{{map(take(sortBy(63.records; 'fields.salePrice'; 'desc'); 5); concat(fields.title, ' - $', fields.salePrice))}}

Generated by Automated Auction Assistant
{{formatDate(now; 'YYYY-MM-DD HH:mm:ss')}}

mapper.text:
📊 WEEKLY PERFORMANCE SUMMARY 📊

💰 Total Revenue: ${{sum(70.records[].fields.revenue)}}
📈 Total Profit: ${{sum(70.records[].fields.profit)}}
🎯 Average ROI: {{round(average(70.records[].fields.roi) * 100; 1)}}%
🏆 Items Won: {{sum(70.records[].fields.itemsWon)}}
✅ Items Sold: {{sum(70.records[].fields.itemsSold)}}
📊 Win Rate: {{round(average(70.records[].fields.winRate) * 100; 1)}}%

